projectile

Class Projectile

  • java.lang.Object
    • gameObject.GameObject
      • gameObject.MovableObject
        • projectile.Projectile
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    Projectile_blackBeam, Projectile_bossFire, Projectile_Building, Projectile_Fire, Projectile_PinkArrow, Projectile_SaDash, Projectile_Scissors, Projectile_SpawnEffect, Projectile_ThornBall, Projectile_Thunder, Projectile_TiroFinale

    public abstract class Projectile
extends MovableObject
    Description:
    Defines Projectile that travels across the screen
    Depends on coordinates on grid map and travels with a certain speed
    The projectile is capable of damaging characters
    Since:
    2014-03-31
    Version:
    1.0
    Author:
    Team 6
